COMMENT ON COLUMN ppdm.well_drill_report.report_id
    IS 'DRILLING REPORT IDENTIFIER: Well drilling reports are often prepared and provided as summaries that cover one or more tours or shifts. All the tours (shifts) contained in a report must be for the same well. Reports for different wells should be captured as different reports.';

