COMMENT ON COLUMN ppdm.well_pressure.well_test_type
    IS 'WELL TEST TYPE: identifies the general type of test used to evaluate the potential of the well. For example, Drill St em Tests (DST), Repeat Formation Tests (RFT), Initial Potential(IP).';

COMMENT ON COLUMN ppdm.well_pressure.row_changed_by
